about.title: What's up!
about.subtitle: What drives you? What are you passionate about? And once you figure that out, what are you going to do about it?
about.description: Answering these questions is something I've found to be pivotal in understanding who I am, where I am, and what I'm doing in a world with overwhelming amount of information. As a software developer, surely you'd think I would be someone that wants to keep creating software and going deeper down that rabbit hole.
